          "detail": "dispatch_slash 只做三件事：确认 / 前缀，用 shlex 拆命令名和参数，按 name 查 _registry。未知命令返回 handled=True 的本地错误。",
          "position": { "x": 300, "y": 70 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 180 }
        },
        {
          "id": "registry",
          "kind": "data",
